Package: discovr
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Tutorials and Materials to Accompany "Discovering Statistics Using R and RStudio"" (Field 2021)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andy", "Field", email = "andyf@sussex.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Andy Field <andyf@sussex.ac.uk>
Description: Interactive R tutorials, datasets, materials and problem solutions for the textbook "Discovering Statistics Using R and RStudio" (Field, 2021).
    Interactive tutorials cover general workflow in R and RStudio, summarizing data, visualizing data, fitting models and bias, correlation, the general linear model, 
    moderation, mediation, missing values, .
License: GPL-3
